                         Malevolent Creations III
 
                @{"  The Encrypted Message of 3203383518  " link "what"}


    We take absolutely no responsibility whatever the buttons below may
 cause to your health, sanity, mother or something else, if you press them.
    If you are not interested in your life as it is now, just go ahead.
                    You will never be the same. Never.

                           YOU HAVE BEEN WARNED

